'''Hummus''', also '''hoummus''', '''hommus''', '''hommous''', is a blend of [[Cookbook:Tahini|sesame seed paste]] and either [[Cookbook:Chickpea|chickpea]] paste or [[Cookbook:Fava Bean|fava bean]] paste. This cookbook has three different recipes for Hummus:
