This is the '''Wikibooks Guide to Unix Computing''', or for short, '''Guide to Unix'''. It describes [[w:Unix|Unix]] and Unix-like systems for ''users'' and ''system administrators''. We include a '''[[Guide to Unix/Commands|guide to commands]]''' which lists several of the common shell commands.
